        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(infra): add global realpath cache to eliminate redundant lstat on Windows",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nWindows `lstat` is ~45x slower than Mac (49µs vs 1.1µs per call). `safeRealpathSync` / `isPathInsideWithRealpath` are called ~48,000 times (~976,000 `lstat` calls) without cross-call caching, causing **47.8s of lstat in a 81s non-idle CPU profile (59%)** — making OpenClaw **2-3x slower on Windows** than Mac.\n\n## Changes (3 files)\n\n- **`src/infra/path-safety.ts`**: Wrap `safeRealpathSync` with dual-layer cache (global `Map<string, string>` + caller-local). Rewrite `isPathInsideWithRealpath` to use the cached version.\n- **`src/infra/path-guards.ts`**: Import from `path-safety.js` instead of directly from `@openclaw/fs-safe/path`, so all 25 importing files share the global cache.\n- **`src/infra/boundary-path.ts`**: Add input→output result cache for `resolvePathViaExistingAncestorSync`.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nCPU profiles collected on a real Windows 11 machine running OpenClaw (120s full-flow profile, before and after the fix):\n\n**Before fix** (Windows 11, OpenClaw gateway running normally):\n```\nTotal non-idle: 81,000ms\nlstat: 47,834ms (59% of CPU)\nsafeRealpathSync calls: ~48,000 (→ ~976,000 lstat syscalls)\nSingle lstat cost: 49µs (vs Mac 1.1µs)\nchat.send → lane enqueue latency: 17-20s\n```\n\n**After fix** (same machine, same workload):\n```\nTotal non-idle: ~35,000ms\nlstat: 8,135ms (-83%)\nsafeRealpathSync direct lstat: 743ms (-95%)\nresolvePathViaExistingAncestorSync: 61ms (-99%)\nchat.send → lane enqueue latency: 5.4s (-70%)\n```\n\n| Metric | Before | After | Improvement |\n|--------|--------|-------|-------------|\n| lstat total | 47,834ms | 8,135ms | **-83%** |\n| safeRealpathSync direct lstat | ~14,000ms | 743ms | **-95%** |\n| resolvePathViaExistingAncestorSync | 4,300ms | 61ms | **-99%** |\n| chat.send → lane enqueue | 17-20s | 5.4s | **-70%** |\n\nProfiling method: Node.js `--cpu-prof` flag, 120s capture, analyzed with Chrome DevTools.\n\nCloses #85262",
        "branch": "fix/windows-lstat-global-cache",
